data.description: This charming two-story home features three bedrooms and three bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. The spacious design allows for an open and airy atmosphere throughout the house. The first floor includes a well-appointed kitchen, a cozy living room, a formal living area, and a dining area perfect for entertaining guests. Upstairs, you'll find the three bedrooms, each offering privacy and tranquility. The master bedroom comes with an en-suite bathroom for added convenience. The property boasts a stylish exterior and includes an oversized backyard for relaxation and outdoor activities. With its thoughtful layout and modern amenities, this home is an ideal blend of comfort and style. Schedule your showing and make this your new home this new year TODAY!
